body: Hello, running a basic EnergyPlus simualtion I got a sever error (even multiple). This is the screen capture. It's Honeybee 0.0.59. Anyone knows what can be the problem? Thank you. Francesco [](http://api.ning.com:80/files/plrPJj-5FY-gjoGTEEBvklZDMD5rADcTVzzHcQWAYB9AkYRKavIWHNLA2Nh-SmzrkKQ-he8VXNdI5cfLfvZrvENLMr7DFTbE/eerror.jpg)

replies.body:
Francesco,

I reported this a few days ago. See [this](https://github.com/mostaphaRoudsari/Honeybee/issues/464).

It is supposed to be fixed by now. Please update your components.

-A.
Thanks! I also updated the files on Food4Rhino to make sure this is not going to show up in more cases.
